The paper deals with the transmission of control signals over a digital communication channel, which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The use of LTI filters and AWGN channels suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the networked control systems (cs.NI) sub-category. The numerical example and simulations indicate that the paper may involve some computational aspects, which could place it in the machine learning (cs.MA) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
